import Login_page from './frontend/Login/Login_page'
import Signup from './frontend/Signup/Signup'
import React from 'react';
import './App.css'
import {Route, Routes} from "react-router-dom"

function App() {
  return <Routes>
    <>
      <Route path></Route>
      <Login_page/>
      <Signup/>
    </>
    </Routes>
}

export default App;
